inventory.name: 707 Detergent Cake
inventory.description: Unleash the superior cleaning power of the 707 Detergent Cake, your essential solution for tackling ground-in dirt and stubborn stains. Engineered with a high-performance, concentrated formula, this robust cleaning bar easily cuts through grease, mud, oil, and tough collar grime. It is the perfect tool for pre-treating heavily soiled areas, providing targeted application that lifts stains before machine or hand washing. The 707 Detergent Cake is designed for remarkable longevity and value; its dense structure resists quick dissolution, making it highly economical. It generates a rich, easy-rinse lather, leaving fabrics fresh and spotless without damaging fibers. Upgrade your laundry routine with this professional-grade stain fighter and experience uncompromising clean.
